org.stekikun.dolmen.unparam

Class Production.Actual

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.stekikun.dolmen.unparam.Production.Item
      • org.stekikun.dolmen.unparam.Production.Actual
  • Enclosing class:
    Production

    public static final class Production.Actual
extends Production.Item
    Represents an actual production item, i.e. a terminal or a non-terminal item.

    The production item can optionally be bound to some Java identifier, in which case the associated value is made available in the enclosing production's semantic action.
